data.description: Opportunity Awaits! This charming 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is brimming with potential. Situated in a desirable neighborhood, this fixer-upper is perfect for the savvy buyer looking to customize and restore a diamond in the rough. The property features a spacious primary bedroom, a large backyard, and a kitchen that opens to the dinning room and living room. While it needs some TLC and renovations, this home offers a great canvas for your vision and a fantastic investment opportunity. Don't miss your chance to transform this house into the home of your dreams. Bring your ideas and make it your own!
